<div class = "thecap" align = "left">H√¨nh 1: Matrix Projection cho Dimensionality Reduction. D·ªØ li·ªáu ban ƒë·∫ßu l√† c√°c c·ªôt c·ªßa ma tr√¢n \(\mathbf{X}\). Ma tr·∫≠n \(\mathbf{P}\in \mathbb{R}^{K\times D}\) l√†m nhi·ªám v·ª• <em>chi·∫øu</em> m·ªói c·ªôt c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n d·ªØ li·ªáu xu·ªëng m·ªôt kh√¥ng gian m·ªõi c√≥ s·ªë chi·ªÅu √≠t h∆°n. D·ªØ li·ªáu m·ªõi ƒë∆∞·ª£c cho trong ma tr·∫≠n \(\mathbf{C}\).</div>
