<p><a name="-principal-component-analysis"></a></p>

<h2 id="3-principal-component-analysis">3. Principal Component Analysis</h2>
<p>C√°ch ƒë∆°n gi·∫£n nh·∫•t ƒë·ªÉ gi·∫£m chi·ªÅu d·ªØ li·ªáu t·ª´ \(D\) v·ªÅ \(K &lt; D\) l√† ch·ªâ gi·ªØ l·∫°i \(K\) ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ <em>quan tr·ªçng nh·∫•t</em>. Tuy nhi√™n, vi·ªác l√†m n√†y ch·∫Øc ch·∫Øn ch∆∞a ph·∫£i t·ªët nh·∫•t v√¨ ch√∫ng ta ch∆∞a bi·∫øt x√°c ƒë·ªãnh th√†nh ph·∫ßn n√†o l√† quan tr·ªçng h∆°n. Ho·∫∑c trong tr∆∞·ªùng h·ª£p x·∫•u nh·∫•t, l∆∞·ª£ng th√¥ng tin m√† m·ªói th√†nh ph·∫ßn mang l√† nh∆∞ nhau, b·ªè ƒëi th√†nh ph·∫ßn n√†o c≈©ng d·∫´n ƒë·∫øn vi·ªác m·∫•t m·ªôt l∆∞·ª£ng th√¥ng tin l·ªõn.</p>

<p>Tuy nhi√™n, n·∫øu ch√∫ng ta c√≥ th·ªÉ bi·ªÉu di·ªÖn c√°c vector d·ªØ li·ªáu ban ƒë·∫ßu trong m·ªôt h·ªá c∆° s·ªü m·ªõi m√† trong h·ªá c∆° s·ªü m·ªõi ƒë√≥, <em>t·∫ßm quan tr·ªçng</em> gi·ªØa c√°c th√†nh ph·∫ßn l√† kh√°c nhau r√µ r·ªát, th√¨ ch√∫ng ta c√≥ th·ªÉ b·ªè qua nh·ªØng th√†nh ph·∫ßn √≠t quan tr·ªçng nh·∫•t.</p>

<p>L·∫•y m·ªôt v√≠ d·ª• v·ªÅ vi·ªác c√≥ hai camera ƒë·∫∑t d√πng ƒë·ªÉ ch·ª•p m·ªôt con ng∆∞·ªùi, m·ªôt camera ƒë·∫∑t ph√≠a tr∆∞·ªõc ng∆∞·ªùi v√† m·ªôt camera ƒë·∫∑t tr√™n ƒë·∫ßu. R√µ r√†ng l√† h√¨nh ·∫£nh thu ƒë∆∞·ª£c t·ª´ camera ƒë·∫∑t ph√≠a tr∆∞·ªõc ng∆∞·ªùi mang nhi·ªÅu th√¥ng tin h∆°n so v·ªõi h√¨nh ·∫£nh nh√¨n t·ª´ ph√≠a tr√™n ƒë·∫ßu. V√¨ v·∫≠y, b·ª©c ·∫£nh ch·ª•p t·ª´ ph√≠a tr√™n ƒë·∫ßu c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë∆∞·ª£c b·ªè qua m√† kh√¥ng c√≥ qu√° nhi·ªÅu th√¥ng tin v·ªÅ h√¨nh d√°ng c·ªßa ng∆∞·ªùi ƒë√≥ b·ªã m·∫•t.</p>

<p>PCA ch√≠nh l√† ph∆∞∆°ng ph√°p ƒëi t√¨m m·ªôt h·ªá c∆° s·ªü m·ªõi sao cho th√¥ng tin c·ªßa d·ªØ li·ªáu ch·ªß y·∫øu t·∫≠p trung ·ªü m·ªôt v√†i to·∫° ƒë·ªô, ph·∫ßn c√≤n l·∫°i ch·ªâ mang m·ªôt l∆∞·ª£ng nh·ªè th√¥ng tin. V√† ƒë·ªÉ cho ƒë∆°n gi·∫£n trong t√≠nh to√°n, PCA s·∫Ω t√¨m m·ªôt <a href="https://machinelearningcoban.com/2017/06/07/svd/#-he-truc-giao-va-truc-chuan">h·ªá tr·ª±c chu·∫©n</a> ƒë·ªÉ l√†m c∆° s·ªü m·ªõi.</p>

<p>Gi·∫£ s·ª≠ h·ªá c∆° s·ªü tr·ª±c chu·∫©n m·ªõi l√† \(\mathbf{U}\) v√† ch√∫ng ta mu·ªën gi·ªØ l·∫°i \(K\) to·∫° ƒë·ªô trong h·ªá c∆° s·ªü m·ªõi n√†y. Kh√¥ng m·∫•t t√≠nh t·ªïng qu√°t, gi·∫£ s·ª≠ ƒë√≥ l√† \(K\) th√†nh ph·∫ßn ƒë·∫ßu ti√™n. Quan s√°t H√¨nh 3 d∆∞·ªõi ƒë√¢y:</p>
<hr />

<div class="imgcap">
<img src="/assets/27_pca/pca_idea.png" align="center" width="800" />
</div>

<div class="thecap" align="left">H√¨nh 3: √ù t∆∞·ªüng ch√≠nh c·ªßa PCA: T√¨m m·ªôt h·ªá tr·ª±c chu·∫©n m·ªõi sao cho trong h·ªá n√†y, c√°c th√†nh ph·∫ßn quan tr·ªçng nh·∫•t n·∫±m trong \(K\) th√†nh ph·∫ßn ƒë·∫ßu ti√™n. </div>
<hr />

<p>Quan s√°t h√¨nh v·∫Ω tr√™n v·ªõi c∆° s·ªü m·ªõi \(\mathbf{U} = [\mathbf{U}_K, \bar{\mathbf{U}}_K]\) l√† m·ªôt h·ªá tr·ª±c chu·∫©n v·ªõi \(\mathbf{U}_K\) l√† ma tr·∫≠n con t·∫°o b·ªüi \(K\) c·ªôt ƒë·∫ßu ti√™n c·ªßa \(\mathbf{U}\). V·ªõi c∆° s·ªü m·ªõi n√†y, ma tr·∫≠n d·ªØ li·ªáu c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë∆∞·ª£c vi·∫øt th√†nh:
\[
\mathbf{X} = \mathbf{U}_K \mathbf{Z} + \bar{\mathbf{U}}_K \mathbf{Y} ~~~~ (8)
\]
T·ª´ ƒë√¢y ta c≈©ng suy ra:</p>

<p>\[
\begin{eqnarray}
\left[
\begin{matrix}
\mathbf{Z} \newline \mathbf{Y}
\end{matrix}
\right] =
\left[
\begin{matrix}
\mathbf{U}_K^T \newline \bar{\mathbf{U}}_K^T
\end{matrix}
\right]\mathbf{X}
\Rightarrow
\begin{matrix}
\mathbf{Z} = \mathbf{U}_K^T \mathbf{X} \newline
\mathbf{Y} = \bar{\mathbf{U}}_K^T\mathbf{X}
\end{matrix}
\end{eqnarray} ~~~~ (9)
\]</p>

<p>M·ª•c ƒë√≠ch c·ªßa PCA l√† ƒëi t√¨m ma tr·∫≠n tr·ª±c giao \(\mathbf{U}\) sao cho ph·∫ßn l·ªõn th√¥ng tin ƒë∆∞·ª£c gi·ªØ l·∫°i ·ªü ph·∫ßn m√†u xanh \(\mathbf{U}_K \mathbf{Z}\) v√† ph·∫ßn m√†u ƒë·ªè \(\bar{\mathbf{U}}_K\mathbf{Y}\) s·∫Ω ƒë∆∞·ª£c l∆∞·ª£c b·ªè v√† thay b·∫±ng m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n kh√¥ng ph·ª• thu·ªôc v√†o t·ª´ng ƒëi·ªÉm d·ªØ li·ªáu. N√≥i c√°ch kh√°c, ta s·∫Ω x·∫•p x·ªâ \(\mathbf{Y}\) b·ªüi m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n c√≥ to√†n b·ªô c√°c c·ªôt l√† nh∆∞ nhau. <em>Ch√∫ √Ω r·∫±ng c√°c c·ªôt n√†y c√≥ th·ªÉ ph·ª• thu·ªôc v√†o d·ªØ li·ªáu training nh∆∞ng kh√¥ng ph·ª• thu·ªôc v√†o d·ªØ li·ªáu test, c√°c b·∫°n s·∫Ω th·∫•y r√µ h∆°n khi l·∫≠p tr√¨nh m√† t√¥i s·∫Ω tr√¨nh b√†y trong b√†i ti·∫øp theo</em>. G·ªçi m·ªói c·ªôt ƒë√≥ l√† \(\mathbf{b}\) v√† c√≥ th·ªÉ coi n√≥ l√† bias, khi ƒë√≥, ta s·∫Ω x·∫•p x·ªâ:</p>

<p>\[
\mathbf{Y} \approx \mathbf{b1}^T
\]
Trong ƒë√≥ \(\mathbf{1}^T\in \mathbb{R}^{1 \times N}\) l√† vector h√†ng c√≥ to√†n b·ªô c√°c ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ b·∫±ng 1. Gi·∫£ s·ª≠ ƒë√£ t√¨m ƒë∆∞·ª£c \(\mathbf{U}\), ta c·∫ßn t√¨m \(\mathbf{b}\) tho·∫£ m√£n:
\[
\mathbf{b} = \text{argmin}_{\mathbf{b}} ||\mathbf{Y} - \mathbf{b1}^T||_F^2 = \text{argmin}_{\mathbf{b}} ||\bar{\mathbf{U}}_K^T\mathbf{X} - \mathbf{b1}^T||_F^2
\]</p>

<p>Gi·∫£i ph∆∞∆°ng tr√¨nh ƒë·∫°o h√†m theo \(\mathbf{b}\) c·ªßa h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u b·∫±ng 0:
\[
(\mathbf{b1}^T - \bar{\mathbf{U}}_K^T\mathbf{X})\mathbf{1} = 0 \Rightarrow N\mathbf{b} = \bar{\mathbf{U}}_K^T \mathbf{X1} \Rightarrow \mathbf{b} = \bar{\mathbf{U}}_K^T \bar{\mathbf{x}}
\]</p>

<p>Nh∆∞ v·∫≠y, <strong>vi·ªác t√≠nh to√°n s·∫Ω thu·∫≠n ti·ªán h∆°n nhi·ªÅu n·∫øu vector k·ª≥ v·ªçng \(\bar{\mathbf{x}} = \mathbf{0}\)</strong>. Vi·ªác n√†y c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë·∫°t ƒë∆∞·ª£c n·∫øu ngay t·ª´ ƒë·∫ßu, ch√∫ng ta tr·ª´ m·ªói vector d·ªØ li·ªáu ƒëi vector k·ª≥ v·ªçng c·ªßa to√†n b·ªô d·ªØ li·ªáu. ƒê√¢y ch√≠nh l√† c√°c b∆∞·ªõc ƒë·∫ßu ti√™n c·ªßa PCA.</p>

<p><a name="eqn10"></a></p>

<p>V·ªõi gi√° tr·ªã \(\mathbf{b}\) t√¨m ƒë∆∞·ª£c n√†y, d·ªØ li·ªáu ban ƒë·∫ßu s·∫Ω ƒë∆∞·ª£c x·∫•p x·ªâ v·ªõi:</p>

<p>\[
\mathbf{X} \approx \tilde{\mathbf{X}} = \mathbf{U}_K \mathbf{Z} + \bar{\mathbf{U}}_K \bar{\mathbf{U}}_K^T\bar{\mathbf{x}}\mathbf{1}^T ~~~ (10)
\]</p>

<p>K·∫øt h·ª£p \((8), (9), (10)\) ta ƒë·ªãnh nghƒ©a h√†m m·∫•t m√°t ch√≠nh nh∆∞ sau:
\[
J = \frac{1}{N} || \mathbf{X} - \tilde{\mathbf{X}}||_F^2 = \frac{1}{N} ||\bar{\mathbf{U}}_K \bar{\mathbf{U}}_K^T \mathbf{X} -  \bar{\mathbf{U}}_K \bar{\mathbf{U}}_K^T \bar{\mathbf{x}}\mathbf{1}^T||_F^2 ~~~~ (11)
\]</p>

<p>Ch√∫ √Ω r·∫±ng, n·∫øu c√°c c·ªôt c·ªßa m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n \(\mathbf{V}\) t·∫°o th√†nh m·ªôt h·ªá tr·ª±c chu·∫©n th√¨ v·ªõi m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n \(\mathbf{W}\) b·∫•t k·ª≥, ta lu√¥n c√≥:
\[
||\mathbf{VW}||_F^2 = \text{trace} (\mathbf{W}^T\mathbf{V}^T\mathbf{V} \mathbf{W}) = \text{trace}(\mathbf{W}^T\mathbf{W}) = ||\mathbf{W}||_F^2
\]</p>

<p>V√¨ v·∫≠y h√†m m·∫•t m√°t trong \((11)\) c√≥ th·ªÉ vi·∫øt l·∫°i th√†nh:
\[
\begin{eqnarray}
J &amp;=&amp; \frac{1}{N} || \bar{\mathbf{U}}_K^T (\mathbf{X} -   \bar{\mathbf{x}}\mathbf{1})^T||_F^2 = \frac{1}{N} ||\bar{\mathbf{U}}_K^T\hat{\mathbf{X}} ||_F^2&amp; \newline
&amp;=&amp; \frac{1}{N} ||\hat{\mathbf{X}}^T \bar{\mathbf{U}}_K ||_F^2 =
\frac{1}{N}\sum_{i = K+1}^D ||\hat{\mathbf{X}}^T\mathbf{u}_i ||_2^2&amp; \newline
&amp;=&amp; \frac{1}{N} \sum_{i=K+1}^D \mathbf{u}_i^T\hat{\mathbf{X}}\hat{\mathbf{X}}^T \mathbf{u}_i&amp; \newline
&amp;=&amp; \sum_{i=K+1}^D \mathbf{u}_i^T\mathbf{S} \mathbf{u}_i &amp; (12)
\end{eqnarray}
\]</p>

<p>V·ªõi \(\hat{\mathbf{X}} = \mathbf{X} - \bar{\mathbf{x}}\mathbf{1}^T\) l√† d·ªØ li·ªáu ƒë√£ chu·∫©n ho√° v√† v·ªõi \(\mathbf{S}\) l√† ma tr·∫≠n hi·ªáp ph∆∞∆°ng sai c·ªßa d·ªØ li·ªáu.  Ta g·ªçi ma tr·∫≠n n√†y \(\hat{\mathbf{X}}\) l√† <em>zero-corrected data</em> ho·∫∑c <em>d·ªØ li·ªáu ƒë√£ ƒë∆∞·ª£c chu·∫©n ho√°</em>. C√≥ th·ªÉ nh·∫≠n th·∫•y \(\hat{\mathbf{x}}_n = \mathbf{x}_n - \bar{\mathbf{x}}\).</p>

<p>C√¥ng vi·ªác c√≤n l·∫°i l√† t√¨m c√°c \(\mathbf{u}_i\) ƒë·ªÉ m·∫•t m√°t l√† nh·ªè nh·∫•t. Tr∆∞·ªõc h·∫øt, ch√∫ng ta c√≥ m·ªôt nh·∫≠n x√©t th√∫ v·ªã. Nh·∫Øc l·∫°i ƒë·ªãnh nghƒ©a ma tr·∫≠n hi·ªáp ph∆∞∆°ng sai \(\mathbf{S} = \frac{1}{N} \hat{\mathbf{X}}^T\hat{\mathbf{X}}\). V·ªõi ma tr·∫≠n \(\mathbf{U}\) tr·ª±c giao b·∫•t k·ª≥, thay \(K = 0\) v√†o \((12)\) ta c√≥:</p>

<p>\[
\begin{eqnarray}
L &amp;=&amp; \sum_{i=1}^D \mathbf{u}_i^T\mathbf{Su}_i = \frac{1}{N} ||\hat{\mathbf{X}}^T\mathbf{U}||_F^2 \newline
&amp;=&amp; \frac{1}{N} \text{trace}(\hat{\mathbf{X}}^T\mathbf{U} \mathbf{U}^T \hat{\mathbf{X}}) &amp; (12) \newline
&amp;=&amp; \frac{1}{N} \text{trace} (\hat{\mathbf{X}}^T \hat{\mathbf{X}}) &amp; (13) \newline
&amp;=&amp; \frac{1}{N} \text{trace} (\hat{\mathbf{X}} \hat{\mathbf{X}}^T) &amp; (14) \newline
&amp;=&amp; \text{trace} (\mathbf{S}) = \sum_{i=1}^D \lambda_i &amp; (16)
\end{eqnarray}
\]</p>

<p>V·ªõi \(\lambda_1 \geq \lambda_2 \geq \dots \geq \lambda_D \geq 0\) l√† c√°c tr·ªã ri√™ng c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n n·ª≠a x√°c ƒë·ªãnh d∆∞∆°ng \(\mathbf{S}\). Ch√∫ √Ω r·∫±ng c√°c tr·ªã ri√™ng n√†y l√† th·ª±c v√† kh√¥ng √¢m.</p>

<p><strong>Nh∆∞ v·∫≠y \(L\) kh√¥ng ph·ª• thu·ªôc v√†o c√°ch ch·ªçn ma tr·∫≠n tr·ª±c giao \(\mathbf{U}\)</strong> v√† b·∫±ng t·ªïng c√°c ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ tr√™n ƒë∆∞·ªùng ch√©o c·ªßa \(\mathbf{S}\). N√≥i c√°ch kh√°c, \(L\) ch√≠nh l√† t·ªïng c·ªßa c√°c ph∆∞∆°ng sai theo t·ª´ng th√†nh ph·∫ßn c·ªßa d·ªØ li·ªáu ban ƒë·∫ßu.</p>

<p>V√¨ v·∫≠y, vi·ªác t·ªëi thi·ªÉu h√†m m·∫•t m√°t \(J\) ƒë∆∞·ª£c cho b·ªüi \((13)\) t∆∞∆°ng ƒë∆∞∆°ng v·ªõi vi·ªác t·ªëi ƒëa:
\[
F  = L - J = \sum_{i=1}^K \mathbf{u}_i \mathbf{S} \mathbf{u}_i^T
\]</p>

<!-- V√¨ v·∫≠y, PCA c√≤n ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi l√† ph∆∞∆°ng ph√°p gi·∫£m s·ªë chi·ªÅu d·ªØ li·ªáu sao cho _l∆∞·ª£ng ph∆∞∆°ng sai gi·ªØ l·∫°i l√† l·ªõn nh·∫•t_ (maximum variance). -->

<p><strong>ƒê·ªãnh l√Ω 1:</strong> \(F\) ƒë·∫°t gi√° tr·ªã l·ªõn nh·∫•t b·∫±ng \(\sum_{i=1}^K \lambda_i\) khi \(\mathbf{u}_i\) l√† c√°c vector ri√™ng c√≥ norm 2 b·∫±ng 1 ·ª©ng v·ªõi c√°c tr·ªã ri√™ng n√†y. T·∫•t nhi√™n, ch√∫ng ta kh√¥ng qu√™n ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán tr·ª±c giao gi·ªØa c√°c \(\mathbf{u}_i\).</p>

<p>Ch√∫ √Ω r·∫±ng \(\lambda_i, i = 1, \dots, K\) ch√≠nh l√† \(K\) tr·ªã ri√™ng l·ªõn nh·∫•t c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n hi·ªáp ph∆∞∆°ng sai \(\mathbf{S}\). Tr·ªã ri√™ng l·ªõn nh·∫•t \(\lambda_1\) c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n n√†y c√≤n ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi l√† <em>Th√†nh ph·∫ßn ch√≠nh th·ª© nh·∫•t</em> (First Principal Component), tr·ªã ri√™ng th·ª© hai \(\lambda_2\) c√≤n ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi l√† <em>Th√†nh ph·∫ßn ch√≠nh th·ª© hai</em>, etc. Ch√≠nh v√¨ v·∫≠y, ph∆∞∆°ng ph√°p n√†y c√≥ t√™n g·ªçi l√† <em>Ph√¢n t√≠ch th√†nh ph·∫ßn ch√≠nh</em> - Principal Component Analysis. Ta ch·ªâ gi·ªØ l·∫°i \(K\) th√†nh ph·∫ßn ch√≠nh c·ªßa d·ªØ li·ªáu khi mu·ªën gi·∫£m s·ªë chi·ªÅu d·ªØ li·ªáu. ƒê·ªÉ c√≥ c√°i nh√¨n tr·ª±c quan h∆°n, ch√∫ng ta c√πng theo d√µi H√¨nh d∆∞·ªõi ƒë√¢y:</p>
<hr />

<div>
<table width="100%" style="border: 0px solid white">
    <tr>
        <td width="40%" style="border: 0px solid white" align="center">
        <img style="display:block;" width="100%" src="/assets/27_pca/pca_var.png" />
         <br />
         </td>
        <td width="40%" style="border: 0px solid white" align="justify">
        H√¨nh 4: PCA d∆∞·ªõi g√≥c nh√¨n Th·ªëng k√™. PCA c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë∆∞·ª£c coi l√† ph∆∞∆°ng ph√°p ƒëi t√¨m m·ªôt h·ªá c∆° s·ªü tr·ª±c chu·∫©n ƒë√≥ng vai tr√≤ m·ªôt ph√©p xoay, sao cho trong h·ªá c∆° s·ªü m·ªõi n√†y, ph∆∞∆°ng sai theo m·ªôt s·ªë chi·ªÅu n√†o ƒë√≥ l√† r·∫•t nh·ªè, v√† ta c√≥ th·ªÉ b·ªè qua.
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
</div>
<hr />

<p>Trong kh√¥ng gian ban ƒë·∫ßu v·ªõi c√°c vector c∆° s·ªü m√†u ƒëen \(\mathbf{e}_1, \mathbf{e}_2\), ph∆∞∆°ng sai theo m·ªói chi·ªÅu d·ªØ li·ªáu ƒë·ªÅu l·ªõn. Trong kh√¥ng gian m·ªõi v·ªõi c√°c vector c∆° s·ªü m√†u ƒë·ªè \(\mathbf{u}_1, \mathbf{u}_2\), ph∆∞∆°ng sai theo chi·ªÅu th·ª© hai \(\hat{\sigma}_2\) r·∫•t nh·ªè so v·ªõi \(\hat{\sigma}_1\). ƒêi·ªÅu n√†y nghƒ©a l√† khi chi·∫øu d·ªØ li·ªáu l√™n \(\mathbf{u}_2\) ta ƒë∆∞·ª£c c√°c ƒëi·ªÉm r·∫•t g·∫ßn nhau v√† g·∫ßn v·ªõi k·ª≥ v·ªçng theo chi·ªÅu ƒë√≥. Trong tr∆∞·ªùng h·ª£p n√†y, k·ª≥ v·ªçng theo m·ªçi chi·ªÅu b·∫±ng 0 n√™n ta c√≥ th·ªÉ thay th·∫ø to·∫° ƒë·ªô theo chi·ªÅu \(\mathbf{u}_2\) b·∫±ng 0. R√µ r√†ng l√†  n·∫øu d·ªØ li·ªáu c√≥ ph∆∞∆°ng sai c√†ng nh·ªè theo m·ªôt chi·ªÅu n√†o ƒë√≥ th√¨ khi x·∫•p x·ªâ chi·ªÅu ƒë√≥ b·∫±ng m·ªôt h·∫±ng s·ªë, sai s·ªë x·∫£y ra c√†ng nh·ªè. PCA th·ª±c ch·∫•t l√† ƒëi t√¨m m·ªôt ph√©p xoay t∆∞∆°ng ·ª©ng v·ªõi m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n tr·ª±c giao sao cho trong h·ªá to·∫° ƒë·ªô m·ªõi, t·ªìn t·∫°i c√°c chi·ªÅu c√≥ ph∆∞∆°ng sai nh·ªè m√† ta c√≥ th·ªÉ b·ªè qua; ta ch·ªâ c·∫ßn gi·ªØ l·∫°i c√°c chi·ªÅu/th√†nh ph·∫ßn kh√°c quan tr·ªçng h∆°n. Nh∆∞ ƒë√£ ch·ª©ng minh ·ªü tr√™n, t·ªïng ph∆∞∆°ng sai theo m·ªçi chi·ªÅu trong h·ªá c∆° s·ªü n√†o c≈©ng l√† nh∆∞ nhau v√† b·∫±ng t·ªïng c√°c tr·ªã ri√™ng c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n hi·ªáp ph∆∞∆°ng sai. V√¨ v·∫≠y, PCA c√≤n ƒë∆∞·ª£c coi l√† ph∆∞∆°ng ph√°p gi·∫£m s·ªë chi·ªÅu d·ªØ li·ªáu m√† gi·ªØ ƒë∆∞·ª£c t·ªïng ph∆∞∆°ng sai c√≤n l·∫°i l√† l·ªõn nh·∫•t.</p>

<p>T√¥i s·∫Ω b·ªè qua ph·∫ßn ch·ª©ng minh c·ªßa ƒê·ªãnh l√Ω 1. Tuy nhi√™n, c≈©ng n√™u m·ªôt v√†i √Ω ƒë·ªÉ b·∫°n ƒë·ªçc c√≥ th·ªÉ h√¨nh dung:</p>

<p>Khi \(K = 1\). Ta c·∫ßn gi·∫£i b√†i to√°n:
\[
\begin{eqnarray}
\max_{\mathbf{u}_1} &amp;\mathbf{u}_1^T\mathbf{S} \mathbf{u}_1 \newline
\text{s.t.:} &amp;||\mathbf{u}_1||_2 = 1
\end{eqnarray}
\]</p>

<p>Nh∆∞ ƒë√£ ƒë·ªÅ c·∫≠p ·ªü ph√≠a tr√™n, h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u ƒë·∫°t gi√° tr·ªã l·ªõn nh·∫•t b·∫±ng \(\lambda_1\) khi \(\mathbf{u}_1\) l√† m·ªôt vector ri√™ng c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n hi·ªáp ph∆∞∆°ng sai \(\mathbf{S}\) t∆∞∆°ng ·ª©ng v·ªõi tr·ªã ri√™ng \(\lambda_1\). V·∫≠y ƒë·ªãnh l√Ω ƒë√∫ng v·ªõi \(K = 1\)</p>

<p>Gi·∫£ s·ª≠ \(\mathbf{u}_1\) ƒë√£ l√† vector ri√™ng ·ª©ng v·ªõi tr·ªã ri√™ng l·ªõn nh·∫•t c·ªßa \(\mathbf{S}\) th·∫ø th√¨ nghi·ªám \(\mathbf{u}_2\) c·ªßa b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u:
\[
\begin{eqnarray}
\max_{\mathbf{u}_2} &amp;\mathbf{u}_2^T\mathbf{S} \mathbf{u}_2 &amp;\newline
\text{s.t.} &amp;||\mathbf{u}_2||_2 = 1 &amp; (21)\newline
&amp; \mathbf{u}_2^T \mathbf{u}_1 = 0 &amp;
\end{eqnarray}
\]
l√† m·ªôt vector ri√™ng c·ªßa \(\mathbf{S}\) ·ª©ng v·ªõi tr·ªã ri√™ng l·ªõn th·ª© hai \(\lambda_2\) c·ªßa n√≥. Ch√∫ √Ω r·∫±ng \(\lambda_2\) c√≥ th·ªÉ b·∫±ng \(\lambda_1\) n·∫øu kh√¥ng gian ri√™ng ·ª©ng v·ªõi \(\lambda_1\) c√≥ s·ªë rank l·ªõn h∆°n 1.</p>

<p>Nh·∫≠n ƒë·ªãnh n√†y c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë∆∞·ª£c ch·ª©ng minh b·∫±ng ph∆∞∆°ng ph√°p nh√¢n t·ª≠ Lagrange. Th·∫≠t v·∫≠y, Lagrangian c·ªßa b√†i to√°n \((21)\) l√†:
\[
\mathcal{L}( \mathbf{u}_2, \nu_1, \nu_2) = \mathbf{u}_2^T\mathbf{S} \mathbf{u}_2 + \nu_1\mathbf{u}_1^T\mathbf{u}_2 + \nu_2(1 - \mathbf{u}_2^T\mathbf{u}_2)
\]</p>

<p>Ta c·∫ßn gi·∫£i h·ªá ph∆∞∆°ng tr√¨nh ƒë·∫°o h√†m c·ªßa \(\mathcal{L}\) theo t·ª´ng bi·∫øn b·∫±ng 0:
\[
\begin{eqnarray}
\frac{\partial \mathcal{L}}{\partial \mathbf{u}_2} &amp;=&amp; 2 \mathbf{Su}_2 + \nu_1 \mathbf{u}_1 - 2\nu_2\mathbf{u}_2 = 0 &amp; (22)\newline
\frac{\partial \mathcal{L}}{\partial \nu_1} &amp;=&amp; \mathbf{u}_1^T \mathbf{u}_2 = 0 &amp; (23)\newline
\frac{\partial \mathcal{L}}{\partial \nu_2} &amp;=&amp; 1 - \mathbf{u}_2^T \mathbf{u}_2 = 0 &amp;(24)\newline
\end{eqnarray}
\]</p>

<p>Nh√¢n c·∫£ hai v·∫ø c·ªßa \((22)\) v·ªõi \(\mathbf{u}_1^T\) v√†o b√™n tr√°i ta c√≥:
\[
2\mathbf{u}_1^T\mathbf{Su}_2 + \nu_1 = 0
\]
V√¨ \(\mathbf{Su}_1 = \lambda_1 \mathbf{u}_1 \Rightarrow \mathbf{u}_1^T\mathbf{Su}_2 = \lambda_1 \mathbf{u}_1^T\mathbf{u}_2 = 0\). T·ª´ ƒë√≥ suy ra \(\nu_1 = 0\) v√† \((22)\) l√∫c n√†y t∆∞∆°ng ƒë∆∞∆°ng v·ªõi:
\[
\mathbf{Su}_2 = \nu_2\mathbf{u}_2 \Rightarrow \mathbf{u}_2^T\mathbf{S} \mathbf{u}_2 = \nu_2
\]
V·∫≠y \(\mathbf{u}_2\) l√† m·ªôt vector ri√™ng c·ªßa \(\mathbf{S}\) ·ª©ng v·ªõi \(\nu_2\). V√† ƒë·ªÉ h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u ƒë·∫°t gi√° tr·ªã l·ªõn nh·∫•t, \(\nu_2\) c·∫ßn c√†ng l·ªõn c√†ng t·ªët. ƒêi·ªÅu n√†y d·∫´n ƒë·∫øn \(\nu_2\) ph·∫£i l√† tr·ªã ri√™ng th·ª© hai c·ªßa \(\mathbf{S}\).</p>

<p>L·∫≠p lu·∫≠n t∆∞∆°ng t·ª±, ta c√≥ th·ªÉ ch·ª©ng minh ƒë∆∞·ª£c: N·∫øu \(\mathbf{u}_i, i = 1, 2, \dots, k-1\) l√† c√°c vector ri√™ng ·ª©ng v·ªõi tr·ªã ri√™ng l·ªõn th·ª© \(i\) c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n n·ª≠a x√°c ƒë·ªãnh d∆∞∆°ng \(\mathbf{S}\), h∆°n n·ªØa, \(k-1\) vector ri√™ng n√†y t·∫°o th√†nh m·ªôt h·ªá tr·ª±c chu·∫©n, th·∫ø th√¨:</p>

<p>\[
\begin{eqnarray}
\max_{\mathbf{u}_k} &amp; \mathbf{u}_k^T\mathbf{Su}_k \newline
\text{s.t.} &amp; \mathbf{u}_k^T\mathbf{u}_k = 1; \newline
&amp; \mathbf{u}_k^T\mathbf{u}_i = 1, i = 1,\dots, k -1
\end{eqnarray}
\]
b·∫±ng ƒë√∫ng v·ªõi tr·ªã ri√™ng ti·∫øp theo \(\lambda_k\) t·∫°i \(\mathbf{u}_k\) l√† vector ri√™ng ·ª©ng v·ªõi tr·ªã ri√™ng n√†y.</p>

<p><a name="-cac-buoc-thuc-hien-pca"></a></p>

<h2 id="4-c√°c-b∆∞·ªõc-th·ª±c-hi·ªán-pca">4. C√°c b∆∞·ªõc th·ª±c hi·ªán PCA</h2>
<p>T·ª´ c√°c suy lu·∫≠n ph√≠a tr√™n, ta c√≥ th·ªÉ t√≥m t·∫Øt l·∫°i c√°c b∆∞·ªõc trong PCA nh∆∞ sau:</p>

<ol>
  <li>T√≠nh vector k·ª≥ v·ªçng c·ªßa to√†n b·ªô d·ªØ li·ªáu:
\[
\bar{\mathbf{x}} = \frac{1}{N} \sum_{n=1}^N \mathbf{x}_n
\]</li>
  <li>Tr·ª´ m·ªói ƒëi·ªÉm d·ªØ li·ªáu ƒëi vector k·ª≥ v·ªçng c·ªßa to√†n b·ªô d·ªØ li·ªáu:
\[
\hat{\mathbf{x}}_n = \mathbf{x}_n - \bar{\mathbf{x}}
\]</li>
  <li>T√≠nh ma tr·∫≠n hi·ªáp ph∆∞∆°ng sai:
\[
\mathbf{S} = \frac{1}{N}\hat{\mathbf{X}}\hat{\mathbf{X}}^T
\]</li>
  <li>T√≠nh c√°c tr·ªã ri√™ng v√† vector ri√™ng c√≥ norm b·∫±ng 1 c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n n√†y, s·∫Øp x·∫øp ch√∫ng theo th·ª© t·ª± gi·∫£m d·∫ßn c·ªßa tr·ªã ri√™ng.</li>
  <li>Ch·ªçn \(K\) vector ri√™ng ·ª©ng v·ªõi \(K\) tr·ªã ri√™ng l·ªõn nh·∫•t ƒë·ªÉ x√¢y d·ª±ng ma tr·∫≠n \(\mathbf{U}_K\) c√≥ c√°c c·ªôt t·∫°o th√†nh m·ªôt h·ªá tr·ª±c giao. \(K\) vectors n√†y, c√≤n ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi l√† c√°c th√†nh ph·∫ßn ch√≠nh, t·∫°o th√†nh m·ªôt kh√¥ng gian con <em>g·∫ßn</em> v·ªõi ph√¢n b·ªë c·ªßa d·ªØ li·ªáu ban ƒë·∫ßu ƒë√£ chu·∫©n ho√°.</li>
  <li>Chi·∫øu d·ªØ li·ªáu ban ƒë·∫ßu ƒë√£ chu·∫©n ho√° \(\hat{\mathbf{X}}\) xu·ªëng kh√¥ng gian con t√¨m ƒë∆∞·ª£c.</li>
  <li>D·ªØ li·ªáu m·ªõi ch√≠nh l√† to·∫° ƒë·ªô c·ªßa c√°c ƒëi·ªÉm d·ªØ li·ªáu tr√™n kh√¥ng gian m·ªõi.
\[
\mathbf{Z} = \mathbf{U}_K^T\hat{\mathbf{X}}
\]</li>
</ol>

<p>D·ªØ li·ªáu ban ƒë·∫ßu c√≥ th·ªÉ t√≠nh ƒë∆∞·ª£c x·∫•p x·ªâ theo d·ªØ li·ªáu m·ªõi nh∆∞ sau:
\[
\mathbf{x} \approx \mathbf{U}_K\mathbf{Z} + \bar{\mathbf{x}}
\]</p>

<p>C√°c b∆∞·ªõc th·ª±c hi·ªán PCA c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë∆∞·ª£c xem trong H√¨nh d∆∞·ªõi ƒë√¢y:</p>

